" Notes:
" - Mappings to <Action> don't work with noremap, source: https://github.com/JetBrains/ideavim?tab=readme-ov-file#executing-actions

" Use H and L for beginning/end of line
map H ^
map L $

" Use J and K to move text blocks in visual mode
map J <Action>(MoveLineDown)
map K <Action>(MoveLineUp)

" Redo
map U <Action>($Redo)
